While I am no longer running for office, I am still committed to the cause of liberty and a world set free in our lifetime.

I'd like to thank my volunteers and campaign staff for their efforts and support. We are in the process of returning donations so those funds may be used to support other Libertarian candidates, if those donors so choose.

As of today, I am ending my campaign for US Senate. I entered this race to help secure ballot access for Libertarians in the state of New Hampshire, but after thoughtful consideration, we do not see a clear path to achieving victory.
